{"title":"角落","date":"2020-04-06T02:20:54.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 6, 2020","L":"04/06/2020","MM-DD":"04-06"},"author":"白桦树下的人","thumbnail":"https://cdn.wardzhou.art/img/cat-2129340_640.jpg","link":"2020/04/06/角落","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-04-07T09:42:30.583Z","content":"<p>把自己放在床上<br>\n找一个舒适的角落<br>\n闭上眼</p>\n<p>一道烛火照亮了这儿<br>\n那长满青草的赤丘<br>\n泛起昏黄的光晕<br>\n掺着火柴和松香的味道<br>\n微微刺鼻却令人醉迷</p>\n<p>深夜的冷气不甘地褪去<br>\n留下的只是那一处<br>\n松软而温暖的角落</p>\n<p>伴随着火光<br>\n还有那缓缓的律动<br>\n发出一声满足的嘟哝<br>\n把自己埋向更深处</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>2020.04.06 深夜<br>\n故城</p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"山桃","link":"2020/04/10/山桃"},"next":{"title":"AdobeXD和Axure PR 9安装及汉化","link":"2020/03/23/installAxure"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2020/04/06/角落/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦树下的人","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"April 7, 2020"}}